fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">praise Him. We talk of temporal things because we have an interest in </div><div class="t me4 xa he y147 ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them. We talk of our friends because we love them; our joys and our </div><div class="t m15d xa he y148 ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sorrows are bound up with them. Yet we have infinitely greater reason </div><div class="t m15e xa he y149 ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to love God than to love our earthly friends; it should be the most </div><div class="t m15f xa he y14a ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">natural thing in the world to make Him first in all our thoughts, to talk </div><div class="t m160 xa he y14b ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of His goodness and tell of His </div><div class="t m161 x63 he y14c ff7 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power.&quot;—Steps to Christ, </div><div class="t m162 x4d he y14c ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 102. </div><div class="t m160 x26 he y14d ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Merely to tell of His power and goodness is not enough. For those </div><div class="t m163 xa he y14e ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who can sing, the beautiful song &quot;How Great Thou Art&quot; is easy to </div><div class="t m164 xa he y14f ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">present; but when the words are real within us, we do more than sing or </div><div class="t m165 xa he y150 ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tell it, we look for ways to </div><div class="t m131 x64 he y150 ff7 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">demonstrate </div><div class="t m166 x15 he y150 ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it. </div><div class="t m167 x65 h2a y151 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">List some of the persons with whom you will interact this </div><div class="t m168 x3f h2a y152 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">week and think of specific ways you might help them under-</div><div class="t m169 x3f h2a y153 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stand the goodness and greatness of God. </div><div class="t m16a x4c he y154 ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.